AddonId: DLsiteMetadata
Type: MetadataProvider
Name: DLsite Metadata
Author: Mysterken
InstallerManifestUrl: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Mysterken/DLsiteMetadata/refs/heads/master/manifests/InstallerManifest.yaml
SourceUrl: https://github.com/Mysterken/DLsiteMetadata
IconUrl: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Mysterken/DLsiteMetadata/master/source/Resources/DLsiteLogo.png
ShortDescription: A plugin that fetches metadata from DLsite.
Description: |-
    This plugin fetches the metadata of a game from DLsite. It supports multiple languages and multiple game categories (e.g., Maniax, Soft).
    It supports directly fetching a game by its work ID or by its link.

    **Supported metadata fields:**
    * Age Rating
    * Background Image
    * Community Score
    * Cover Image
    * Description
    * Developers
    * Genres
    * Icon
    * Links
    * Name
    * Publishers
    * Release Date
    * Series
Tags: [Metadata, DLsite]
Links:
    GitHub: https://github.com/Mysterken/DLsiteMetadata
